<span id="freeTextContainer11568204038964027204">I have read this book at least 6 times over time. I&apos;ve indicated the last date I read it. It is my all time favorite. The story is about a young woman in the distant future from a far away planet who is dissillusioned after finding out she can never be a solo singer due to a latent burr in her voice. She travels to another planet and becomes a part of an unusual ecosystem by singing to and with Crystal rock formations. This crystals are used in communication and spaceship drive systems. Well wri</span>
  <span id="freeText11568204038964027204" style="display:none">I have read this book at least 6 times over time. I've indicated the last date I read it. It is my all time favorite. The story is about a young woman in the distant future from a far away planet who is dissillusioned after finding out she can never be a solo singer due to a latent burr in her voice. She travels to another planet and becomes a part of an unusual ecosystem by singing to and with Crystal rock formations. This crystals are used in communication and spaceship drive systems. Well written and filled with imagery and drama.<br /><br />I am reading this book again for the 7th time...summer of 2009. I'm not sure why I like it so much except it's very creative and about a strong woman. :)</span>
